{"id":274509,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-常州拆迁访民状告市建设局、法庭上无对/","date":"2013-01-14T10:16:11Z","modified":"2013-01-14T10:16:11Z","title":"维权网 | 常州拆迁访民状告市建设局、法庭上无对等待遇（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div align=\"left\"><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span>1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日上午</span><span>，常州拆迁访民控告当地市建设局和开发商的案子在天宁区法院十五庭审理，多位拆迁访民要求旁听庭审、学习法律，但是法庭仅仅只给拆迁访民十张旁听证，市建设局方面却没有人数限制，几个法警硬把坚持要求旁听的拆迁户拖出，并锁上十五庭大门。</span></p>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>位法警把拆迁户的旁听者阻拦在庭大门外，来参加旁听的老太太实在支撑不住，坐在法庭门口的垃圾箱上。普通百姓学习法律的热情如此高涨，法院却很抗拒。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>在法庭审理中，有拆迁户询问天宁法院院长的办公电话，却始终无法问到，另外天宁区法院的领导始终不肯讲自己姓什么，是担任什么职位的，难道这些都是机密？</span><span></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-JTmwCzsfExA/UPOyUN_PEkI/AAAAAAAAY38/eEso_Nn9HR8/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-JTmwCzsfExA/UPOyUN_PEkI/AAAAAAAAY38/eEso_Nn9HR8/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"239\" /></a></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span><br /></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}